import {Row,Col} from 'antd'
import '../static/css/choose.css'

function Choose(){
    return (
        <>
            <Row>
                广告位
            </Row>
            <Row className="choose_middle" gutter={4}>
                <Col span={10}>
                    nanshe
                </Col>
                <Col span={10}>
                nvse
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </>
    )
}
export default Choose
